<http://model.geneontology.org/ev_w_id_R-HSA-2395801_RO_0002411_R-HSA-2396594_Reactome_R-HSA-2424491_R-HSA-2395801_enabled_by_UniProt_P43405_R-HSA-2395801_controller_R-HSA-2396594_enabled_by_UniProt_P06239_R-HSA-2396594_controller>
